title: NoMeansNo -  Live at Slim's, San Francisco CA 10-29-06
description:
For the fans of Nomeansno, please know the band allows taping of concerts and does not mind sharing of any live shows in any file sharing format.  Please visit the www.nomeanswhatever.com message board for information on more live show swapping.

This bootleg comes from video shot by a fan of the band and ripped to MP3 from DVD.  Fairly decent sound quality.
